},{"d":"गवाक्षः","m":"Gavaksha"},{"d":"कुमुदः","m":"Kumuda"},{"d":"तथा","m":"likewise"},{"d":"नलः","m":"Nala"},{"d":"अथ","m":"and पनसः Panasa"},{"d":"अमित्रविषयम्","m":"at the enemy city"},{"d":"प्राप्ताः","m":"having reached"},{"d":"समवेताः","m":"collected"},{"d":"समर्थयन्","m":"thought."}]},{"v":4,"dev":"इयंसालक्षयतेलङ्कापुरीरावणपालिता ।सासुरोरगगन्धर्वैरमरैरपिदुर्जया","trans":"\"This Lanka city ruled by Ravana is seen. It appears that this city is unconquerable to Devas, demons and Gandharvas also by the immortals.\"","words":[{"d":"रावणपालिता","m":"ruled by Ravana"},{"d":"सासुरोरगगन्धर्वैः","m":"Devas, demons and Gandharvas"},{"d":"अमरैरपि","m":"immortals"},{"d":"दुर्जया","m":"not conquerable"},{"d":"सा","m":"that"},{"d":"इयम्","m":"this"},{"d":"लङ्कापुरी","m":"Lanka city"},{"d":"लक्षयते","m":"appears."}]},{"v":5,"dev":"कार्यसिद्धिंपुरस्कृत्यमन्द्रयध्वंविनिर्णये ।नित्यंसन्निहितोह्यत्ररावणोराक्षसाधिपः","trans":"\"Rakshasa king Ravana is ever present here. Prepare yourself to achieve success in the mission and determine your duty.\"","words":[{"d":"कार्यसिद्धिम्","m":"to achieve success"},{"d":"पुरस्कृत्य","m":"preparing"},{"d":"विनिर्णये","m":"determining duty"},{"d":"अत्र","m":"there"},{"d":"राक्षसाधिपः","m":"Rakshasa king"},{"d":"रावणः","m":"Ravana"},{"d":"नित्यम्","m":"ever"},{"d":"सन्निहितःहि","m":"present here."}]},{"v":6,"dev":"तथातेषुब्रुवाणेषुरावणावरजोऽब्रवीत् ।वाक्यमग्राम्यपदवत्पुष्कलार्धंविभीषणः","trans":"While they were speaking like that to one another, Ravana's brother Vibheeshana spoke courteously, words full of meaning.","words":[{"d":"तथा","m":"like that"},{"d":"तेषु","m":"they"},{"d":"ब्रुवाणेषु","m":"speaking to one another"},{"d":"रावणावरजः","m":"Ravana's brother"},{"d":"विभीषणः","m":"Vibheeshana"},{"d":"अग्राम्यपदवत्","m":"courteous words"},{"d":"पुष्कलार्थम्","m":"meaningful"},{"d":"वाक्यम्","m":"words"},{"d":"अब्रवीत्","m":"spoke."}]},{"v":7,"dev":"अनलश्शरभश्चैवसम्पातिःप्रघसस्तथा ।गत्वालङ्कांममामात्याःपुरींपुनरिहागताः","trans":"\"My ministers Anala, Sarabha, Sampathi and also Praghasa went to Lanka and saw it and returned.\"","words":[{"d":"मम","m":"my"},{"d":"अमात्याः","m":"ministers"},{"d":"अनलः","m":"Anala"},{"d":"शरभश्चैव","m":"and Sarabha"},{"d":"सम्पातिः","m":"Sampathi"},{"d":"तथा","m":"so also"},{"d":"प्रघसः","m":"Praghasa"},{"d":"लङ्कांपुरीम्","m":"to Lanka city"},{"d":"गत्वा","m":"went"},{"d":"पुनः","m":"again"},{"d":"इह","m":"there"},{"d":"आगताः","m":"came"}]},{"v":8,"dev":"भूत्वाशकुनयस्सर्वेप्रविष्टाश्चरिपोर्भलम् ।विधानंविहितंयच्चतद्धृष्टवासमुपस्थिताः","trans":"All of them assumed the form of birds and went deep into Lanka, saw the enemy strength and arrangements made by the enemy and turned up.","words":[{"d":"सर्वे","m":"all"},{"d":"शकुनयः","m":"birds"},{"d":"भूत्वा","m":"form"},{"d":"रिपोः","m":"enemy"},{"d":"बलम्","m":"strength"},{"d":"प्रविष्टाः","m":"went in deep"},{"d":"विधानम्","m":"arrangements"},{"d":"विहितम्","m":"knowing"},{"d":"तत्","m":"there"},{"d":"दृष्टवा","m":"seeing"},{"d":"समुपस्थिताः","m":"turned up."}]},{"v":9,"dev":"संविधानंयथाहुस्तेरावणस्यदुरात्मनः ।राम तद्ब्रुवतस्सर्वंयथात्त्वेनमेशृणु","trans":"\"Rama! Alas, they told me everything of the way evil minded Ravana's army is organized as it is. Listen to me.\"","words":[{"d":"राम","m":"Rama"},{"d":"ते","m":"to you"},{"d":"दुरात्मनः","m":"evil minded"},{"d":"रावणस्य","m":"Ravana 's"},{"d":"संविधानम्","m":"army is organized"},{"d":"यथा","m":"that way"},{"d":"आहुः","m":"alas"},{"d":"सर्वम्","m":"everything"},{"d":"याथात्त्वेन","m":"as it is"},{"d":"ब्रुवतः","m":"told"},{"d":"मे","m":"to me"},{"d":"शृणु","m":"listen."}]},{"v":10,"dev":"पूर्वंप्रहस्तस्सबलोद्वारमासाद्यतिष्ठति ।दक्षिणंचमहावीर्यौमहापार्श्वमहोदरौ","trans":"\"Powerful Prahasta stands at east gate with army, Mahaparsva and Mahodara of great valour are at the south gate.\"","words":[{"d":"प्रबलः","m":"powerful"},{"d":"प्रहस्तः","m":"Prahasta"},{"d":"पूर्वंद्वारम्","m":"at east gate"},{"d":"आसाद्य","m":"with army"},{"d":"तिष्ठति","m":"remains"},{"d":"महावीर्यौ","m":"of great valour"},{"d":"महापार्श्वमहोदरौ","m":"Mahaparsva and Mahodara"},{"d":"दक्षइणंच","m":"at south gate"}]},{"v":11,"dev":"इन्द्रजित्पश्चिमंद्वारंराक्षसैर्भहुभिर्वृतः ।पट्टसासिधनुष्मद्भिश्शूलमुद्गरपाणिभिः नानाप्रहरणैश्शूरैरावृतोरावणात्मजः ।","trans":"\"Ravana's own son, Indrajith stands at the west gate surrounded by numerous Rakshasas collected together wielding sharp swords, bows, spears, arrows and darts and many kinds of weapons.\"","words":[{"d":"रावणात्मजः","m":"Ravana's own son"},{"d":"इन्द्रजित्","m":"Indrajith"},{"d":"पट्टसासिधनुष्मद्भिः","m":"sharp iron words, bows and spears"},{"d":"शोलमुद्गरपाणिभिः","m":"arrows and darts"},{"d":"बहुभिः","m":"numerous"},{"d":"राक्षसैः","m":"Rakshasas"},{"d":"वृतः","m":"surrounded by"},{"d":"नानाप्रहरणैः","m":"many kinds of weapons"},{"d":"शूरैः","m":"heroes"},{"d":"आवृतः","m":"collected together"},{"d":"पश्चिमंद्वारम्","m":"west gate."}]},{"v":12,"dev":"राक्षसानांसहस्रैस्तुबहुभिश्शस्त्रपाणिभिः युक्तःपरमसंविग्नोराक्षर्भहुभिर्वृतः ।उत्तरंनगरद्वारंरावणस्स्वयमास्थितः","trans":"\"Ravana himself stands at the north gate of Lanka, highly agitated surrounded by many thousands of Rakshasas wielding weapons.\"","words":[{"d":"रावणः","m":"Ravana"},{"d":"शस्त्रपाणिभिः","m":"wielding weapons"},{"d":"राक्षसानाम्","m":"with Rakshasas"},{"d":"बहुभिः","m":"many"},{"d":"वृतः","m":"surrounded by"},{"d":"सहस्रैः","m":"thousands"},{"d":"युक्तः","m":"skilled"},{"d":"राक्षसैः","m":"Rakshasas"},{"d":"परमसंविग्नः","m":"highly agitated"},{"d":"उत्तरम्","m":"north"},{"d":"नगरद्वारम्","m":"gate of the city"},{"d":"स्वयम्","m":"himself"},{"d":"आस्थितः","m":"stands."}]},{"v":13,"dev":"राक्षसानांसहस्रैस्तुबहुभिश्शस्त्रपाणिभिः युक्तःपरमसंविग्नोराक्षर्भहुभिर्वृतः ।उत्तरंनगरद्वारंरावणस्स्वयमास्थितः","trans":"\"Ravana himself stands at the north gate of Lanka, highly agitated surrounded by many thousands of Rakshasas wielding weapons.\"","words":[{"d":"रावणः","m":"Ravana"},{"d":"शस्त्रपाणिभिः","m":"wielding weapons"},{"d":"राक्षसानाम्","m":"with Rakshas